Set up a chat channel with some trusted people from this server, the petition a GM to establish that the logs don't show such a transfer, and report the finding to the people in the channel.  I'm sure that if you really are a victem, this would be the best way to clear up your name.  If the GM didn't respond right away, ask for them to contact various people other than yourself with the results when they come in.<br>
